  `build/efo.owl` was built without MONDO terms, causing 27 MONDO terms       
  referenced in `components/subclasses.owl` to appear as \"dangling\" (with   
  only `owl:Thing` as parent).\n\nFixed in commit 8c94821 by restoring        
  `\u003cowl:imports rdf:resource=\"http://www.ebi.ac.                        
  uk/efo/imports/mondo_import.owl\"/\u003e` to the correct position in the    
  ontology header."                                                           
